snippet.title: The Ascent | Cyber Heist DLC | OUT NOW!
snippet.description:
Indents! The Cyber Heist DLC is out now!

Completed The Ascent but are itching for more? Cyber Heist is for you! Solo or in co-op with your friends, take on new challenging missions, explore brand new environments, fight your way against new enemies, and experience new ways of fighting using melee weapons!

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1802470/The_Ascent__Cyber_Heist/
Xbox: https://www.microsoft.com/store/r/9n8llt05053f
PlayStation: https://store.playstation.com/concept/233248
